tags.name: meme-maker
tags.description:
`meme-maker`
Connects lrndesign-gallery to HAX

Events:

  * `i18n-manager-register-element` {`CustomEvent<{ namespace: string; localesPath: string; locales: string[]; }>`} - 

Attributes:

  * `described-by` {`string`} - Aria-describedby data passed down to appropriate tag

  * `image-url` {`string`} - url to the meme image

  * `top-text` {`string`} - Text on top of the image.

  * `bottom-text` {`string`} - Bottom text for the image.

  * `alt` {`string`} - Alt data passed down to appropriate tag

Properties:

  * `describedBy` {`string`} - Aria-describedby data passed down to appropriate tag

  * `topText` {`string`} - Text on top of the image.

  * `bottomText` {`string`} - Bottom text for the image.

  * `alt` {`string`} - Alt data passed down to appropriate tag
